  Added gnuconfig_update to detect mips systems properly

  14 Nov 2003; Aron Griffis <agriffis@gentoo.org> ORBit-0.5.17.ebuild:
  Stable on ia64

  28 Oct 2003; Bartosch Pixa <darkspecter@gentoo.org> ORBit-0.5.17.ebuild:
  set ppc in keywords

  28 Oct 2003; foser <foser@gentoo.org> ORBit-0.5.{6,7}.ebuild :
  Fix SRC_URI by using gnome.org eclass (#32103)

